RIL-428: Add External Ingress for Stage Environment

* Automation Testers will use external ingress url to run automation test scenarios in Stage.
* We will be temporarily adding IPs to allow list in hof-services-config.
* This is the only safest approach to provide access to Jenkins servers running on EBSA platform

